{"tid":2158851,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"我整左隻game係Steam上左架 但身邊啲人叫我打份工算2","createTime":"2020-08-16T03:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T06:19:56.000Z","uid":65139,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50fb4bb8136efc04872fcf15436da55d67b78cfc","tid":2158851,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇端專訪講一隻Indie驚叫 《Legendary Knight》（中譯：傳奇騎士）<br />\n一開頭覺得有啲熟口面好似邊到聽過，懷疑都係連登咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果睇到一半先發覺真係：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《Legendary Knight》2020年3月在Steam上架，至7月底，大約已有1600人購買。遊戲剛推出時，約有六成玩家來自法國，大木估計這是因為遊戲被法國 youtuber賞識，拍片介紹。<strong>到6月，大木在LIHKG討論區發帖，名為「我整左隻game係Steam上左架 但身邊啲人叫我打份工算」</strong>（我開發的遊戲已經在Steam上架，但身邊人還是叫我去打工），由此開始獲得香港網民關注，加上網絡節目《星期三港案》7月訪問大木，來自香港本地的玩家越來越多，現時有6成玩家為香港人。</strong><br />\n<br />\n我冇打機，連steam都冇裝，但對於呢個post就幾有記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以純碎覺得件事好神奇好有緣，所以抄返巴打個post出post<br />\n<br />\n想講任何做緊/支持緊Indie/香港/本地創作/文化etc...嘅手足要繼續努力<br />\n你嘅付出其實係默默影響緊其他人以至個社會，會有好多你估唔到Karma/Butterfly effect架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸：<br />\n呢個月前開始訂「端」，日日追兩三篇深度追到好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但見佢講中港台/文化都幾有質素同全面，見有端高質post都想share下做下打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWAikLS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWAikLS.png&h=6292e1e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/202008016-game-on-lengendary-knight/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F202008016-game-on-lengendary-knight%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=36a9e11e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/202008016-game-on-lengendary-knight/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;小智既爸爸&ldquo;巴打見字回 我睇完你專訪呀 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9866bff6a1d2da03dfd6aa5486461cbad40372","tid":2158851,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:31:30.000Z","msg":"我整左隻game係Steam上左架 但身邊啲人叫我打份工算<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2057530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2057530</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6d2cbe0ba914972889cd24143b95cc229881522","tid":2158851,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec9866bff6a1d2da03dfd6aa5486461cbad40372","tid":2158851,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:31:30.000Z","msg":"我整左隻game係Steam上左架 但身邊啲人叫我打份工算<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2057530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2057530</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"唔記得quote返巴打原post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55871a6b0e0d1828226fa99a8900b5d3a7d58d8","tid":2158851,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:16:41.000Z","msg":"即買左"},{"pid":"ca9c54a0d240e8c73d34d923e942df8da8ed885d","tid":2158851,"uid":8373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n玩左一陣 幾難玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93eaae768413fc4778deeb45d19667f77657b5f9","tid":2158851,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:10:52.000Z","msg":"跟"},{"pid":"d4f66918e8c9f6fcf6536c87c8d7b885b89956f3","tid":2158851,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c